  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Optical coherence tomography is technology widely used in medicine. In this study, the
      investigators will use an optical tomographic scanner to scan skin tissue image.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will use optical tomographic scanner to scan skin specimen and obtain
      tissue images. Part of skin specimen obtained from skin biopsy or surgery will be scanned.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
